en: utter_greet
mt: utter_greet

en: Hi! Welcome to Cartesio! I'm here to help you. Ask me whatever you need.
mt: Hi! Merħba għal Cartesio! Jien hawn biex ngħinek. Staqsini dak kollu li għandek bżonn.

en: utter_please_rephrase
mt: utter_please_rephrase

en: Fallback for intents. No intent has higher enough confidence to be choosen.
mt: Fallback għall-intenzjonijiet. L-ebda intenzjoni ma għandha fiduċja ogħla biżżejjed biex tintgħażel.

en: utter_default
mt: utter_default

en: Fallback for utterances. The bot does not know which utterance present to the user.
mt: Fallback għal kliem. Il-bot ma jafx liema kelma tippreżenta lill-utent.

en: utter_regist-docs.why
mt: utter_regist-docs.why

en: The identity document asked is needed to verify your identity.
mt: Id-dokument tal-identità mitlub huwa meħtieġ biex tivverifika l-identità tiegħek.

en: We ask your {identity_document_slot} because we need to verify your identity.
mt: Aħna nistaqsu lill-{identity_document_slot} tiegħek għax għandna bżonn nivverifikaw l-identità tiegħek.

en: utter_regist-docs.accepted
mt: utter_regist-docs.accepted

en: The accepted documents are the identity card and the passport.
mt: Id-dokumenti aċċettati huma l-karta tal-identità u l-passaport.

en: Yes, the {identity_document_slot} is an accepted identity document.
mt: Iva, l-{identity_document_slot} huwa dokument tal-identità aċċettat.

en: utter_regist-docs.formats
mt: utter_regist-docs.formats

en: You can upload every file and there is no size limit.
mt: Tista 'ttella' kull fajl u m'hemm l-ebda limitu ta' daqs.

en: utter_regist-docs.expired
mt: utter_regist-docs.expired

en:
The document must be sent at the time of the registration and it has to be valid for at least three months from the registration date. 
If your document expires earlier you have to wait for its renewal.
mt:
Id-dokument irid jintbagħat fil-ħin tar-reġistrazzjoni u għandu jkun validu għal mill-inqas tliet xhur mid-data tar-reġistrazzjoni. 
Jekk id-dokument tiegħek jiskadi qabel trid tistenna għat-tiġdid tiegħu.

en: utter_regist-docs.error-generic
mt: utter_regist-docs.error-generic

en: To solve this error, send an email to the support at support@framont.com.
mt: Biex issolvi dan l-iżball, ibgħat email lill-appoġġ fuq support@framont.com.

en: utter_regist-docs.residence-proof
mt: utter_regist-docs.residence-proof

en: The proof of residence is a document that shows and confirms the residency address you inserted in the registration phase.
mt: Il-prova tar-residenza hija dokument li juri u jikkonferma l-indirizz tar-residenza li daħħalt fil-fażi tar-reġistrazzjoni.

en: utter_regist-docs.residence-proof-valid-list
mt: utter_regist-docs.residence-proof-valid-list

en: These are all the documents valid as a proof of residence: LIST OF ACCEPTED PROOF OF RESIDENCE.
mt: Dawn huma d-dokumenti kollha validi bħala prova ta' residenza: LISTA TA' PROVA TA' RESIDENZA AĊĊETTATA.

en: utter_regist-docs.upload-modify
mt: utter_regist-docs.upload-modify

en: To modify or replace an already uploaded document you can use the "Upload a new document or add a front/rear page" that you can find in the Identity Documents page.
mt: Biex timmodifika jew tissostitwixxi dokument li diġà ttella' tista' tuża l-"Ttella' dokument ġdid jew żid paġna ta' quddiem/wara" li tista' ssib fil-paġna Dokumenti tal-Identità.

en: utter_regist-docs.check
mt: utter_regist-docs.check

en:
One of our operators will check that all documentation you provided is ok. 
You will receive a feedback usually within 2 working days.
mt:
Wieħed mill-operaturi tagħna se jiċċekkja li d-dokumentazzjoni kollha li pprovdejt hija tajba. 
Int ser tirċievi feedback normalment fi żmien jumejn tax-xogħol.

en: utter_regist-docs.residence-list
mt: utter_regist-docs.residence-list

en: These are all the documents are valid as well as a proof of residence: bank statements, utility bills, letters from government, credit card statements, house purchase deed.
mt: Dawn huma d-dokumenti kollha huma validi kif ukoll prova ta 'residenza: rendikonti bankarji, kontijiet ta' utilità, ittri mill-gvern, dikjarazzjonijiet ta 'karta ta' kreditu, att tax-xiri tad-dar.

en: utter_regist-docs.residence-verify
mt: utter_regist-docs.residence-verify

en: These are all the documents valid as a proof of residence: LIST OF ACCEPTED PROOF OF RESIDENCE.
mt: Dawn huma d-dokumenti kollha validi bħala prova ta' residenza: LISTA TA' PROVA TA' RESIDENZA AĊĊETTATA.

en:
The proof of residence you indicated is a valid document. 
These are all the documents valid as a proof of residence: LIST OF ACCEPTED PROOF OF RESIDENCE.
mt:
Il-prova tar-residenza li indikajt hija dokument validu. 
Dawn huma d-dokumenti kollha validi bħala prova ta' residenza: LISTA TA' PROVA TA' RESIDENZA AĊĊETTATA.
